"help.text"
msgid "As native file picker dialogs of the window manager of your operating system."
msgstr "ເປັນໄດອາລັອກເລືອກໄຟລ໌ມາດຕະຖານຂອງລະບົບປະຕິບັດການຂອງທ່ານ."

#. WLoj9
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id561669373655721\n"
"help.text"
msgid "As built-in %PRODUCTNAME file picker dialogs."
msgstr "ເປັນໄດອາລັອກເລືອກໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມາພ້ອມກັບ %PRODUCTNAME."

#. TWsL9
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id371669373673552\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>Tools - Options</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010600.xhp\"> - <menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME</menuitem> - <menuitem>General</menuitem></link> to shift from one to the other."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - ຄວາມມັກ</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010600.xhp\"> - <menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME</menuitem> - <menuitem>ທົ່ວໄປ</menuitem></link> ເພື່ອປ່ຽນຈາກແບບໜຶ່ງໄປຫາອີກແບບໜຶ່ງ."

#. 5CT67
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3150713\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the file that you want to open contains styles, <link href=\"text/shared/01/01020000.xhp#templates\">special rules</link> apply."
msgstr "ຖ້າໄຟລ໌ທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເປີດມີຮູບແບບ, <link href=\"text/shared/01/01020000.xhp#templates\">ກົດເກນພິເສດ</link> ຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້."

#. VYDoj
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id221669046989152\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Folder selection"
msgstr "ການເລືອກໂຟນເດີ"

#. bbFZB
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id831669136604534\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Pick up your preferred folder from the pull-down list or type its path name. <emph>Autocomplete</emph> function can be used to ease typing."
msgstr "ເລືອກໂຟນເດີທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຈາກລາຍການ ຫຼື ພິມຊື່ເສັ້ນທາງ. ສາມາດໃຊ້ຟັງຊັນ <emph>ຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນອັດຕະໂນມັດ</emph> ເພື່ອໃຫ້ພິມໄດ້ງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. MAC4G
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id271669379646668\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Connect to a server using the <link href=\"text/shared/guide/cmis-remote-files-setup.xhp\">File Services</link> dialog.<br/> Select a parent folder from the folder path with <image id=\"img_id3149415\" src=\"svtools/res/up_small.png\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id3149415\">Icon Open</alt></image>."
msgstr "ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບເຊີບເວີໂດຍໃຊ້ໄດອາລັອກ <link href=\"text/shared/guide/cmis-remote-files-setup.xhp\">ການບໍລິການໄຟລ໌</link>.<br/> ເລືອກໂຟນເດີຫຼັກຈາກເສັ້ນທາງໂຟນເດີດ້ວຍ <image id=\"img_id3149415\" src=\"svtools/res/up_small.png\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id3149415\">ໄອຄອນເປີດ</alt></image>."

#. 6EPPW
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id231669379647930\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Add a subfolder to the current folder with <image id=\"img_id3149415\" src=\"res/fp015.svg\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id3145149\">create new folder</alt></image>."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມໂຟນເດີຍ່ອຍໃສ່ໂຟນເດີປັດຈຸບັນດ້ວຍ <image id=\"img_id3149415\" src=\"res/fp015.svg\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id3145149\">ສ້າງໂຟນເດີໃໝ່</alt></image>."

#. 274aP
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148538\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Places and Files"
msgstr "ສະຖານທີ່ ແລະ ໄຟລ໌"

#. D6GAi
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id871669134861416\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Add current folder to your favorite places using <widget>+</widget>. Remove a selected place from the list with <widget>-</widget>."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມໂຟນເດີປັດຈຸບັນໃສ່ສະຖານທີ່ທີ່ມັກໂດຍໃຊ້ <widget>+</widget>. ລົບສະຖານທີ່ທີ່ເລືອກອອກຈາກລາຍການດ້ວຍ <widget>-</widget>."

#. iYhsL
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3156113\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FILEDLG_STANDARD\">Displays the files and folders in the folder that you are in.</ahelp> Click column headers to sort files names, types, sizes or dates in ascending or descending order."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FILEDLG_STANDARD\">ສະແດງໄຟລ໌ ແລະ ໂຟນເດີໃນໂຟນເດີທີ່ທ່ານຢູ່.</ahelp> ຄລິກທີ່ສ່ວນຫົວຖັນເພື່ອຈັດຮຽງຊື່ໄຟລ໌, ປະເພດ, ຂະໜາດ ຫຼື ວັນທີ ຕາມລໍາດັບຈາກໜ້ອຍໄປຫາຫຼາຍ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍໄປຫາໜ້ອຍ."

#. iUNpS
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3159256\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To open more than one document at the same time, each in an own window, hold <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><widget>Command</widget></caseinline><defaultinline><widget>Ctrl</widget></defaultinline></switchinline> while you click the files, and then click <widget>Open</widget>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເປີດເອກະສານຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງອັນພ້ອມກັນ, ໂດຍແຕ່ລະອັນຢູ່ໃນໜ້າຕ່າງຂອງຕົນເອງ, ໃຫ້ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><widget>Command</widget></caseinline><defaultinline><widget>Ctrl</widget></defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ທ່ານຄລິກໄຟລ໌, ແລ້ວຄລິກ <widget>ເປີດ</widget>."

#. fGGBD
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id341547247820173\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Modern system file dialogs present many features for file handling. Most allows you to rename, delete, create files, sort list of files, display files and folders in icons, tree or list views, traverse the file system folder tree and much more. Use the mouse right button to get a list of commands on the selected files in the display area."
msgstr "ໄດອາລັອກໄຟລ໌ຂອງລະບົບທີ່ທັນສະໄໝມີຄຸນສົມບັດຫຼາຍຢ່າງສໍາລັບການຈັດການໄຟລ໌. ສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ທ່ານປ່ຽນຊື່, ລຶບ, ສ້າງໄຟລ໌, ຈັດຮຽງລາຍການໄຟລ໌, ສະແດງໄຟລ໌ ແລະ ໂຟນເດີໃນຮູບແບບໄອຄອນ, ແຜນຜັງຕົ້ນໄມ້ ຫຼື ລາຍການ ແລະ ອື່ນໆອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ. ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມຂວາຂອງເມົາສ໌ເພື່ອເບິ່ງລາຍການຄໍາສັ່ງສໍາລັບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກໃນພື້ນທີ່ສະແດງ."

#. fDrb4
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153331\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"svt/ui/querydeletedialog/yes\" visibility=\"hidden\">Click to delete the file with the name shown in this dialog.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"svt/ui/querydeletedialog/yes\" visibility=\"hidden\">ຄລິກເພື່ອລຶບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຊື່ສະແດງຢູ່ໃນໄດອາລັອກນີ້.</ahelp>"

#. xdn8x
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3161458\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"svt/ui/querydeletedialog/no\" visibility=\"hidden\">Click to cancel deletion of the file with the name shown in this dialog.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"svt/ui/querydeletedialog/no\" visibility=\"hidden\">ຄລິກເພື່ອຍົກເລີກການລຶບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຊື່ສະແດງຢູ່ໃນໄດອາລັອກນີ້.</ahelp>"

#. FbYoj
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3147531\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"svt/ui/querydeletedialog/all\" visibility=\"hidden\">Click to delete all selected files.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"svt/ui/querydeletedialog/all\" visibility=\"hidden\">ຄລິກເພື່ອລຶບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກທັງໝົດ.</ahelp>"

#. CYgpk
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154280\n"
"help.text"
msgid "File name"
msgstr "ຊື່ໄຟລ໌"

#. AP3aC
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3161656\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"fpicker/ui/explorerfiledialog/file_name\">Enter a file name or a path for the file.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"fpicker/ui/explorerfiledialog/file_name\">ປ້ອນຊື່ໄຟລ໌ ຫຼື ເສັ້ນທາງສຳລັບໄຟລ໌.</ahelp>"

#. 9FPNV
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id61547286521877\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following features are available in the dialog:"
msgstr "ຄຸນສົມບັດຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ໃນໄດອາລັອກ:"

#. 9V9k2
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150767\n"
"help.text"
msgid "File type"
msgstr "ປະເພດໄຟລ໌"

#. GZh7y
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153969\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"fpicker/ui/explorerfiledialog/file_type\">Select the file type that you want to open, or select <emph>All Files (*)</emph> to display a list of all of the files in the folder.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"fpicker/ui/explorerfiledialog/file_type\">ເລືອກປະເພດໄຟລ໌ທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເປີດ, ຫຼື ເລືອກ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ທັງໝົດ (*)</emph> ເພື່ອສະແດງລາຍການໄຟລ໌ທັງໝົດໃນໂຟນເດີ.</ahelp>"

#. PtYmp
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145117\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Version"
msgstr "ເວີຊັນ"

#. 7foCQ
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3149291\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FILEOPEN_VERSION\">If there are multiple versions of the selected file, select the version that you want to open.</ahelp> You can save and organize multiple versions of a document by choosing <emph>File - Versions</emph>. The versions of a document are opened in read-only mode."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FILEOPEN_VERSION\">ຖ້າມີຫຼາຍເວີຊັນຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກເວີຊັນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເປີດ.</ahelp> ທ່ານສາມາດບັນທຶກ ແລະ ຈັດລະບຽບເອກະສານຫຼາຍເວີຊັນໄດ້ໂດຍການເລືອກ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ເວີຊັນ</emph>. ເວີຊັນຂອງເອກະສານຈະຖືກເປີດໃນໂໝດອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ."

#. nDYC2
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3144762\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Read-only"
msgstr "ອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ"

#. vFGCv
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3145785\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FILEOPEN_READONLY\">Opens the file in read-only mode.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FILEOPEN_READONLY\">ເປີດໄຟລ໌ໃນໂໝດອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ.</ahelp>"

#. tpAdG
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154125\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open"
msgstr "ເປີດ"

#. Cg5CX
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3152933\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"fpicker/ui/explorerfiledialog/open\">Opens the selected document(s).</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"fpicker/ui/explorerfiledialog/open\">ເປີດເອກະສານທີ່ເລືອກ.</ahelp>"

#. QUhGn
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147085\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Insert"
msgstr "ແຊກ"

#. RoJX8
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3156293\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you opened the dialog by choosing <emph>Insert - Text from File</emph>, the <emph>Open</emph> button is labeled <emph>Insert</emph>. <ahelp hid=\"HID_FILEDLG_INSERT_BTN\">Inserts the selected file into the current document at the cursor position.</ahelp>"
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານເປີດໄດອາລັອກໂດຍການເລືອກ <emph>ແຊກ - ຂໍ້ຄວາມຈາກໄຟລ໌</emph>, ປຸ່ມ <emph>ເປີດ</emph> ຈະຖືກປ່ຽນຊື່ເປັນ <emph>ແຊກ</emph>. <ahelp hid=\"HID_FILEDLG_INSERT_BTN\">ແຊກໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກເຂົ້າໃນເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນຢູ່ຕຳແໜ່ງເຄີເຊີ.</ahelp>"

#. SnxPF
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149984\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Play"
msgstr "ຫຼິ້ນ"

#. St4FN
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3147289\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FILESAVE_DOPLAY\">Plays the selected sound file. Click again to stop playing the sound file.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FILESAVE_DOPLAY\">ຫຼິ້ນໄຟລ໌ສຽງທີ່ເລືອກ. ຄລິກອີກຄັ້ງເພື່ອຢຸດການຫຼິ້ນ.</ahelp>"

#. iDUpN
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149260\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opening Documents With Templates"
msgstr "ການເປີດເອກະສານດ້ວຍແມ່ແບບ"

#. DciWP
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3150105\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you open a document created from a template, %PRODUCTNAME checks to see if the template has been modified since the document was last opened. If the template was changed, a dialog is shown where you can select which styles to apply to the document."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານເປີດເອກະສານທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນຈາກແມ່ແບບ, %PRODUCTNAME ຈະກວດເບິ່ງວ່າແມ່ແບບມີການປ່ຽນແປງຫຼືບໍ່ ນັບຕັ້ງແຕ່ເປີດເອກະສານຄັ້ງຫຼ້າສຸດ. ຖ້າແມ່ແບບມີການປ່ຽນແປງ, ໄດອາລັອກຈະປາກົດຂຶ້ນເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານເລືອກວ່າຈະນຳໃຊ້ຮູບແບບໃດກັບເອກະສານ."

#. JCkDE
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153096\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To apply the new styles from the template to the document, click <widget>Update Styles</widget>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອນຳໃຊ້ຮູບແບບໃໝ່ຈາກແມ່ແບບໃສ່ເອກະສານ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກ <widget>ອັບເດດຮູບແບບ</widget>."

#. BDWYx
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3147581\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To retain the styles that are currently used in the document, click <widget>Keep Old Styles</widget>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຮັກສາຮູບແບບທີ່ໃຊຢູ່ໃນເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກ <widget>ຮັກສາຮູບແບບເກົ່າ</widget>."

#. n4Dm9
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3145367\n"
"help.text"
msgid "%PRODUCTNAME recognizes templates located in any directory defined for <emph>Templates</emph> in <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>Tools - Options</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline><menuitem> - </menuitem><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010300.xhp\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Paths</menuitem></link>."
msgstr "%PRODUCTNAME ຈະຮັບຮູ້ແມ່ແບບທີ່ຢູ່ໃນໄດເລກທໍຣີໃດໜຶ່ງທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ສຳລັບ <emph>ແມ່ແບບ</emph> ໃນ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - ຄວາມມັກ</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline><menuitem> - </menuitem><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010300.xhp\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - ເສັ້ນທາງ</menuitem></link>."

#. Nksvx
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3154988\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If a document was created using a template that cannot be found, a dialog is shown that asks you how to proceed next time the document is opened."
msgstr "ຖ້າເອກະສານຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍໃຊ້ແມ່ແບບທີ່ຫາບໍ່ເຫັນ, ໄດອາລັອກຈະປາກົດຂຶ້ນເພື່ອຖາມວ່າທ່ານຕ້ອງການດຳເນີນການແນວໃດໃນຄັ້ງຕໍ່ໄປທີ່ເປີດເອກະສານ."

#. HzeB3
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3151351\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To break the link between the document and the missing template, click <widget>No</widget>, otherwise <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> will look for the template the next time you open the document."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຕັດການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ລະຫວ່າງເອກະສານ ແລະ ແມ່ແບບທີ່ຫາຍໄປ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກ <widget>ບໍ່</widget>, ບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> ຈະຊອກຫາແມ່ແບບໃນຄັ້ງຕໍ່ໄປທີ່ທ່ານເປີດເອກະສານ."

#. Sm3CJ
#: 01020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020000.xhp\n"
"par_id6930143\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you use <menuitem>File - Save As</menuitem> and select a template filter to save a template in a directory that is <emph>not</emph> specified in the <emph>Templates</emph> path, then the documents based on that template will <emph>not</emph> be checked."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານໃຊ້ <menuitem>ໄຟລ໌ - ບັນທຶກເປັນ</menuitem> ແລະ ເລືອກຕົວກອງແມ່ແບບເພື່ອບັນທຶກແມ່ແບບໃນໄດເລກທໍຣີທີ່ <emph>ບໍ່ໄດ້</emph> ລະບຸໄວ້ໃນເສັ້ນທາງ <emph>ແມ່ແບບ</emph>, ເອກະສານທີ່ອີງຕາມແມ່ແບບນັ້ນຈະ <emph>ບໍ່ຖືກ</emph> ກວດສອບ."

