#. iBEsr
#: 01020103.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01020103.xhp\n"
"par_id3155892\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Ensure that the file extension corresponds to the file type of the document. For example, a Microsoft Word document must have a <emph>*.doc</emph> or <emph>*.docx</emph> extension for $[officename] to use the appropriate filter."
msgstr "ກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າສ່ວນຂະຫຍາຍໄຟລ໌ກົງກັບປະເພດໄຟລ໌ຂອງເອກະສານ. ຕົວຢ່າງ, ເອກະສານ Microsoft Word ຕ້ອງມີສ່ວນຂະຫຍາຍ <emph>*.doc</emph> ຫຼື <emph>*.docx</emph> ເພື່ອໃຫ້ $[officename] ໃຊ້ຕົວກອງທີ່ເໝາະສົມ."

#. e5NCe
#: 01020103.xhp
msgctxt ""
