"par_id3153626\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Enter a file name or a path for the file. You can also enter a <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000002.xhp#url\">URL</link></ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ປ້ອນຊື່ໄຟລ໌ ຫຼື ເສັ້ນທາງສຳລັບໄຟລ໌. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດປ້ອນ <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000002.xhp#url\">URL</link> ໄດ້</ahelp>"

