"01100100.xhp\n"
"par_id3154682\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"sfx/ui/descriptioninfopage/DescriptionInfoPage\">Contains descriptive information about the document.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"sfx/ui/descriptioninfopage/DescriptionInfoPage\">ປະກອບມີຂໍ້ມູນຄຳອະທິບາຍກ່ຽວກັບເອກະສານ.</ahelp>"

#. reSZA
