msgctxt ""
"01100100.xhp\n"
"par_id721712354151660\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <menuitem>File - Properties</menuitem> then select the <menuitem>Description</menuitem> tab."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <menuitem>ໄຟລ໌ - ຄຸນສົມບັດ</menuitem> ຈາກນັ້ນເລືອກແຖບ <menuitem>ຄຳອະທິບາຍ</menuitem>."

#. PSac7
#: 01100100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01100100.xhp\n"
"par_id271712404524124\n"
"help.text"
msgid "%PRODUCTNAME supports the Dublin Core Metadata Element Set, a standardized set of metadata elements used to describe physical and electronic documents."
msgstr "%PRODUCTNAME ຮອງຮັບ Dublin Core Metadata Element Set, ເຊິ່ງເປັນຊຸດອົງປະກອບເມຕາເດຕາມາດຕະຖານທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອອະທິບາຍເອກະສານທາງກາຍະພາບ ແລະ ເອເລັກໂຕຣນິກ."

#. DQhzs
#: 01100100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01100100.xhp\n"
"par_id311712404964926\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can add additional metadata elements in the <link href=\"text/shared/01/01100300.xhp\"><menuitem>Custom Properties</menuitem></link> tab."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມອົງປະກອບເມຕາເດຕາເພີ່ມເຕີມໄດ້ໃນແຖບ <link href=\"text/shared/01/01100300.xhp\"><menuitem>ຄຸນສົມບັດກຳນົດເອງ</menuitem></link>."

#. DB262
#: 01100100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01100100.xhp\n"
"par_id581602083308804\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Title</emph>, <emph>Subject</emph>, and <emph>Keywords</emph> are exported to PDF files as PDF Document Properties. Entered values are exported and will appear in the corresponding fields in the PDF Document Properties Description."
msgstr "<emph>ຊື່ເລື່ອງ</emph>, <emph>ຫົວຂໍ້</emph>, ແລະ <emph>ຄຳສຳຄັນ</emph> ຈະຖືກສົ່ງອອກໄປຫາໄຟລ໌ PDF ເປັນຄຸນສົມບັດເອກະສານ PDF. ຄ່າທີ່ປ້ອນເຂົ້າຈະຖືກສົ່ງອອກ ແລະ ປາກົດຢູ່ໃນຟີວທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງໃນຄຳອະທິບາຍຄຸນສົມບັດເອກະສານ PDF."

