msgctxt ""
"01100100.xhp\n"
"par_id951714495693749\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>DCMI Definition: </emph>An entity responsible for making the resource available."
msgstr "<emph>ຄຳນິຍາມ DCMI: </emph>ໜ່ວຍງານທີ່ຮັບຜິດຊອບໃນການເຮັດໃຫ້ຊັບພະຍາກອນມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້."

