"par_id3153527\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you save a copy of a file that contains version information (by choosing <emph>File - Save As</emph>), the version information is <emph>not</emph> saved with the file."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານບັນທຶກສຳເນົາຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນເວີຊັນ (ໂດຍເລືອກ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ບັນທຶກເປັນ</emph>), ຂໍ້ມູນເວີຊັນນັ້ນຈະ <emph>ບໍ່</emph> ຖືກບັນທຶກໄປພ້ອມກັບໄຟລ໌."

#. ha47E
#: 01190000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01190000.xhp\n"
