"01190000.xhp\n"
"par_id3150466\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"sfx/ui/versioncommentdialog/VersionCommentDialog\">Enter a comment here when you are saving a new version. If you clicked <emph>Show</emph> to open this dialog, you cannot edit the comment.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"sfx/ui/versioncommentdialog/VersionCommentDialog\">ປ້ອນຄຳເຫັນທີ່ນີ້ເມື່ອທ່ານກຳລັງບັນທຶກເວີຊັນໃໝ່. ຖ້າທ່ານຄລິກ <emph>ສະແດງ</emph> ເພື່ອເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບນີ້, ທ່ານຈະບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂຄຳເຫັນໄດ້.</ahelp>"

