msgctxt ""
"01190000.xhp\n"
"par_id3152811\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"sfx/ui/versionsofdialog/compare\">Compare the changes that were made in each version.</ahelp> If you want, you can <link href=\"text/shared/01/02230400.xhp\"><emph>Manage Changes</emph></link>."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"sfx/ui/versionsofdialog/compare\">ປຽບທຽບການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ເກີດຂຶ້ນໃນແຕ່ລະເວີຊັນ.</ahelp> ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການ, ທ່ານສາມາດ <link href=\"text/shared/01/02230400.xhp\"><emph>ຈັດການການປ່ຽນແປງ</emph></link> ໄດ້."

#. 7yFCP
