#. rLmrF
#: 02020000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02020000.xhp\n"
"par_id3157898\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Reverses the action of the last <emph>Undo</emph> command. To select the <emph>Undo</emph> step that you want to reverse, click the arrow next to the <emph>Redo</emph> icon on the <emph>Standard</emph> bar.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ກັບຄືນການກະທຳຂອງຄຳສັ່ງ <emph>ຍົກເລີກ</emph> ສຸດທ້າຍ. ເພື່ອເລືອກຂັ້ນຕອນການ <emph>ຍົກເລີກ</emph> ທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການກັບຄືນ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໃສ່ລູກສອນຢູ່ຂ້າງໄອຄອນ <emph>ເຮັດຄືນ</emph> ເທິງແຖບ <emph>ມາດຕະຖານ</emph>.</ahelp>"

