msgstr "<link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Documentation/How_Tos/Regular_Expressions_in_Writer\">ໜ້າ Wiki ກ່ຽວກັບ regular expressions ໃນ Writer</link>"

#. aWcJb
