#. BXNhF
#: 02110000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02110000.xhp\n"
"par_id3147084\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_GLBLTREE_INSERT\">Inserts a file, an index, or a new document into the master document.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_GLBLTREE_INSERT\">ແຊກໄຟລ໌, ດັດສະນີ ຫຼື ເອກະສານໃໝ່ລົງໃນເອກະສານຫຼັກ.</ahelp>"

#. mdiTw
#: 02110000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02110000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153969\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also insert files into the master document by dragging a file from your desktop and dropping on the master view of the Navigator."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດແຊກໄຟລ໌ລົງໃນເອກະສານຫຼັກໄດ້ໂດຍການລາກໄຟລ໌ຈາກໜ້າຈໍຄອມພິວເຕີ (desktop) ຂອງທ່ານມາປ່ອຍໃສ່ມຸມມອງຫຼັກຂອງຕົວນຳທາງ."

