"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_GLBLTREE_INS_IDX\">Inserts an index or a table of contents into the master document.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_GLBLTREE_INS_IDX\">ແຊກດັດສະນີ ຫຼື ສາລະບານລົງໃນເອກະສານຫຼັກ.</ahelp>"

