#. 3NQkD
#: 02180100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02180100.xhp\n"
"par_id3154751\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"sfx/ui/linkeditdialog/app\">Lists the application that last saved the source file. %PRODUCTNAME applications have the server name <emph>soffice</emph>.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"sfx/ui/linkeditdialog/app\">ສະແດງລາຍການແອັບພລິເຄຊັນທີ່ບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບຄັ້ງຫຼ້າສຸດ. ແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ %PRODUCTNAME ມີຊື່ເຊີບເວີແມ່ນ <emph>soffice</emph>.</ahelp>"

#. KNH5c
