#. HNucX
#: 02180100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02180100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153527\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"sfx/ui/linkeditdialog/file\">Path to the source file. <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000005.xhp#saving\">Relative paths</link> must be expressed by full URI, for example, with <emph>file://</emph>.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"sfx/ui/linkeditdialog/file\">ເສັ້ນທາງຫາໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບ. <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000005.xhp#saving\">ເສັ້ນທາງແບບສຳພັດ</link> ຕ້ອງຖືກສະແດງດ້ວຍ URI ເຕັມ, ຕົວຢ່າງເຊັ່ນ: ດ້ວຍ <emph>file://</emph>.</ahelp>"

#. eEnmT
#: 02180100.xhp
