msgstr "ບັນທຶກສຳເນົາເປັນ"

#. qTemA
#: 02200000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02200000.xhp\n"
"par_id871686147463891\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opens the <link href=\"text/shared/01/01060002.xhp\">Save as</link> dialog to save a copy of the object in a file. The file extension suggested depends on the type of the OLE object."
msgstr "ເປີດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <link href=\"text/shared/01/01060002.xhp\">ບັນທຶກເປັນ</link> ເພື່ອບັນທຶກສຳເນົາຂອງວັດຖຸລົງໃນໄຟລ໌. ນາມສະກຸນໄຟລ໌ທີ່ແນະນຳແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບປະເພດຂອງວັດຖຸ OLE."

#. HB6iE
#: 02200000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02200000.xhp\n"
