msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Resizes the object to the original size.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ປັບຂະໜາດວັດຖຸໃຫ້ເປັນຂະໜາດເດີມ.</ahelp>"

