#. MHBDz
#: 02220000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02220000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150502\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"h1\"><link href=\"text/shared/01/02220000.xhp#imagemap editor\">ImageMap Editor</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"h1\"><link href=\"text/shared/01/02220000.xhp#imagemap editor\">ຕົວແກ້ໄຂແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ (ImageMap Editor)</link></variable>"

#. JbUy9
#: 02220000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02220000.xhp\n"
"par_id3159194\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"imagemaptext\"><ahelp hid=\"svx/ui/imapdialog/ImapDialog\">Allows you to attach URLs to specific areas, called hotspots, on a graphic or a group of graphics. An image map is a group of one or more hotspots.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"imagemaptext\"><ahelp hid=\"svx/ui/imapdialog/ImapDialog\">ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດແນບ URL ໃສ່ພື້ນທີ່ສະເພາະ, ທີ່ເອີ້ນວ່າ hotspots, ເທິງຮູບກຣາຟິກ ຫຼື ກຸ່ມຂອງຮູບກຣາຟິກ. ແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ (Image map) ແມ່ນກຸ່ມຂອງ hotspots ຕັ້ງແຕ່ໜຶ່ງອັນຂຶ້ນໄປ.</ahelp></variable>"

#. qyFGR
#: 02220000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02220000.xhp\n"
"par_id3149751\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can draw three types of hotspots: <emph>rectangles</emph>, <emph>ellipses</emph>, and <emph>polygons</emph>. When you click a hotspot, the URL is opened in the browser window or frame that you specify. You can also specify the text that appears when your mouse rests on the hotspot."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດແຕ້ມ hotspots ໄດ້ສາມປະເພດຄື: <emph>ຮູບສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມ</emph>, <emph>ຮູບວົງລີ</emph> ແລະ <emph>ຮູບຫຼາຍແຈ</emph>. ເມື່ອທ່ານຄລິກໃສ່ hotspot, URL ຈະຖືກເປີດຂຶ້ນໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມບຣາວເຊີ ຫຼື ຂອບ (frame) ທີ່ທ່ານກຳນົດ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດກຳນົດຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນເມື່ອທ່ານວາງເມົາສ໌ໄວ້ເທິງ hotspot ນັ້ນໄດ້."

