"par_id3147261\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"CALC\">You can set the properties of the markup elements by choosing <link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01060600.xhp\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME Calc - Changes</emph></link> in the <emph>Options</emph> dialog box.</caseinline></switchinline>"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"CALC\">ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງອົງປະກອບເຄື່ອງໝາຍໂດຍການເລືອກ <link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01060600.xhp\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME Calc - ການປ່ຽນແປງ</emph></link> ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ຕົວເລືອກ</emph>.</caseinline></switchinline>"

