"par_id3152935\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Accepts the selected change and removes the highlighting from the change in the document.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຍອມຮັບການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ເລືອກ ແລະ ລຶບການເນັ້ນອອກຈາກການປ່ຽນແປງໃນເອກະສານ.</ahelp>"

#. NG3rE
