msgctxt ""
"04100000.xhp\n"
"par_id3145090\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/specialcharacters/subsetlb\">Select a Unicode block for the current font.</ahelp> The special characters for the selected Unicode block are displayed in the character table."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/specialcharacters/subsetlb\">ເລືອກບລັອກຢູນິໂຄດ (Unicode) ສໍາລັບຟອນປັດຈຸບັນ.</ahelp> ອັກສອນພິເສດສໍາລັບບລັອກຢູນິໂຄດທີ່ເລືອກຈະສະແດງໃນຕາຕະລາງອັກສອນ."

