"05020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3148491\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/charnamepage/ctlfontnamelb\">Enter the name of an installed font that you want to use, or select a font from the list.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/charnamepage/ctlfontnamelb\">ປ້ອນຊື່ຂອງຟອນທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງແລ້ວທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຊ້, ຫຼື ເລືອກຟອນຈາກລາຍຊື່.</ahelp>"

