#. oGL33
#: 05020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3150359\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/charnamepage/ctlsizelb\">Enter or select the font size that you want to apply. For scalable fonts, you can also enter decimal values.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/charnamepage/ctlsizelb\">ປ້ອນ ຫຼື ເເລືອກຂະໜາດຟອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການນຳໃຊ້. ສໍາລັບຟອນທີ່ປັບຂະໜາດໄດ້, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດປ້ອນຄ່າທົດສະນິຍົມໄດ້.</ahelp>"

#. t9Gfx
#: 05020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3148797\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you are creating a style that is based on another style, you can enter a percentage value or a point value (for example, <item type=\"input\">-2pt</item> or <item type=\"input\">+5pt</item>)."
msgstr "ຫາກທ່ານກຳລັງສ້າງສະໄຕລ໌ທີ່ອີງໃສ່ສະໄຕລ໌ອື່ນ, ທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນຄ່າເປັນເປີເຊັນ ຫຼື ຄ່າເປັນພອຍ (point) ໄດ້ (ຕົວຢ່າງ: <item type=\"input\">-2pt</item> ຫຼື <item type=\"input\">+5pt</item>)."

#. hJCp6
#: 05020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3151176\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Language"
msgstr "ພາສາ"

#. MGSCA
#: 05020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3157961\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/charnamepage/ctllanglb\">Sets the language that the spellchecker uses for the selected text or the text that you type. Available language modules have a check mark in front of them.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/charnamepage/ctllanglb\">ຕັ້ງຄ່າພາສາທີ່ຕົວສະກົດຄຳໃຊ້ສໍາລັບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ເລືອກ ຫຼື ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ທ່ານພິມ. ໂມດູນພາສາທີ່ມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຈະມີເຄື່ອງໝາຍຖືກຢູ່ທາງໜ້າ.</ahelp>"

#. dyESr
#: 05020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3157962\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the language list consists of an editable combo box, you can enter a valid <emph>BCP 47 language tag</emph> if the language you want to assign is not available from the selectable list."
msgstr "ຫາກລາຍຊື່ພາສາເປັນກ່ອງຄອມໂບທີ່ແກ້ໄຂໄດ້, ທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນ <emph>ແທັກພາສາ BCP 47</emph> ທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງໄດ້ ຫາກພາສາທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການກຳນົດບໍ່ມີຢູ່ໃນລາຍຊື່ທີ່ເລືອກໄດ້."

#. dgRLJ
#: 05020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3157963\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For language tag details please see the <link href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IETF_language_tag\">IETF language tag</link> Wikipedia page and the W3C <link href=\"https://www.w3.org/International/articles/language-tags/\">Language tags in HTML and XML</link> article."
msgstr "ສໍາລັບລາຍລະອຽດແທັກພາສາ ກະລຸນາເບິ່ງໜ້າ Wikipedia <link href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IETF_language_tag\">IETF language tag</link> ແລະ ບົດຄວາມ W3C <link href=\"https://www.w3.org/International/articles/language-tags/\">Language tags in HTML and XML</link>."

#. cpdYi
#: 05020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3153770\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also change the locale setting for cells (choose <emph>Format - Cells - Numbers</emph>)."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດປ່ຽນການຕັ້ງຄ່າທ້ອງຖິ່ນສໍາລັບຫ້ອງໄດ້ (ເລືອກ <emph>ຮູບແບບ - ຫ້ອງ - ຕົວເລກ</emph>)."

#. FASWt
