#. XpACz
#: 05020300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020300.xhp\n"
"par_id3144432\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/numberingformatpage/sourceformat\">Uses the same number format as the cells containing the data for the chart.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/numberingformatpage/sourceformat\">ໃຊ້ຮູບແບບຕົວເລກດຽວກັນກັບຫ້ອງທີ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນສໍາລັບແຜນພູມ.</ahelp>"

