"par_id3148650\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Minute time formats M and MM must be used in combination with hour or second time formats to avoid confusion with month date format."
msgstr "ຮູບແບບເວລານາທີ M ແລະ MM ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ຮ່ວມກັບຮູບແບບເວລາຊົ່ວໂມງ ຫຼື ວິນາທີ ເພື່ອຫຼີກເວັ້ນການສັບສົນກັບຮູບແບບວັນທີຂອງເດືອນ."

#. f9vZ5
#: 05020301.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020301.xhp\n"
"par_id3148649\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If a time is entered in the form 02:03.45 or 01:02:03.45 or 25:01:02, the following formats are assigned if no other time format has been specified: MM:SS.00 or [HH]:MM:SS.00 or [HH]:MM:SS"
msgstr "ຖ້າປ້ອນເວລາໃນຮູບແບບ 02:03.45 ຫຼື 01:02:03.45 ຫຼື 25:01:02, ຮູບແບບດັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ຈະຖືກກຳນົດໃຫ້ ຖ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດຮູບແບບເວລາອື່ນໄວ້: MM:SS.00 ຫຼື [HH]:MM:SS.00 ຫຼື [HH]:MM:SS"

#. Z6w48
#: 05020301.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05020301.xhp\n"
"par_id3148701\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The time can be suffixed with <emph>AM/PM</emph> to have hours in 0-12 AM/PM format."
msgstr "ເວລາສາມາດຕໍ່ທ້າຍດ້ວຍ <emph>AM/PM</emph> ເພື່ອສະແດງຊົ່ວໂມງໃນຮູບແບບ 0-12 AM/PM."

#. biREB
