msgctxt ""
"05030100.xhp\n"
"par_id3151041\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/paraindentspacing/checkCB_AUTO\">Automatically indents a paragraph according to the font size and the line spacing. The setting in the <emph>First Line </emph>box is ignored.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/paraindentspacing/checkCB_AUTO\">ຍໍ້ໜ້າຫຍໍ້ໜ້າໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດຕາມຂະໜາດຟອນ ແລະ ໄລຍະຫ່າງແຖວ. ການຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ແຖວທຳອິດ</emph> ຈະຖືກລະເວັ້ນ.</ahelp>"

