msgid "<link href=\"text/swriter/guide/registertrue.xhp\">Printing with Page line-spacing</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/swriter/guide/registertrue.xhp\">ການພິມດ້ວຍໄລຍະຫ່າງແຖວຂອງໜ້າ</link>"

