#. TxQ7T
#: 05040200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05040200.xhp\n"
"par_id3149827\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/pageformatpage/comboPageFormat\">Select a predefined paper size, or create a custom format by entering the dimensions for the paper in the <emph>Height</emph> and <emph>Width</emph> boxes.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/pageformatpage/comboPageFormat\">ເລືອກຂະໜາດເຈ້ຍທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ລ່ວງໜ້າ, ຫຼື ສ້າງຮູບແບບກຳນົດເອງໂດຍການປ້ອນຂະໜາດຂອງເຈ້ຍໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ຄວາມສູງ</emph> ແລະ <emph>ຄວາມກວ້າງ</emph>.</ahelp>"

#. cbQEJ
#: 05040200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05040200.xhp\n"
"par_id581668003824292\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Slides formats \"On Screen Show (4:3)\", \"On Screen Show (16:9)\" and \"On Screen Show (16:10)\" are used for Microsoft PowerPoint interoperability."
msgstr "ຮູບແບບສະໄລ້ \"ການສະແດງເທິງໜ້າຈໍ (4:3)\", \"ການສະແດງເທິງໜ້າຈໍ (16:9)\" ແລະ \"ການສະແດງເທິງໜ້າຈໍ (16:10)\" ແມ່ນໃຊ້ເພື່ອຄວາມສາມາດໃນການເຮັດວຽກຮ່ວມກັບ Microsoft PowerPoint."

