"par_id3156113\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/pageformatpage/spinHeight\">Displays the height of the selected paper format. To define a custom format, enter a height here.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/pageformatpage/spinHeight\">ສະແດງຄວາມສູງຂອງຮູບແບບເຈ້ຍທີ່ເລືອກ. ເພື່ອກຳນົດຮູບແບບດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນຄວາມສູງຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້.</ahelp>"

#. 9WDK5
