"par_id3154812\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/gradientpage/GradientPage\">Select a gradient, modify the properties of a gradient, or save a new gradient.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/gradientpage/GradientPage\">ເລືອກສີໄລ່ລະດັບ, ແກ້ໄຂຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງສີໄລ່ລະດັບ ຫຼື ບັນທຶກສີໄລ່ລະດັບໃໝ່.</ahelp>"

