msgstr "ຮູບແບບ"

#. PgyUs
#: 05210500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05210500.xhp\n"
"par_id241592868416096\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Tiled</emph>: Fill the area with the image as tiles."
msgstr "<emph>ແບບລຽງຍາຍ (Tiled)</emph>: ເຕີມພື້ນທີ່ດ້ວຍຮູບພາບແບບລຽງຕໍ່ກັນ."

#. gCgdA
