msgid "<emph>Stretched</emph>: Stretch the image to fit the object area."
msgstr "<emph>ແບບດຶງຢືດ</emph>: ດຶງຮູບພາບໃຫ້ພໍດີກັບພື້ນທີ່ວັດຖຸ."

#. MRcQq
#: 05210500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05210500.xhp\n"
"par_id651592868426975\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Custom position/size</emph>: Set a custom size and position of the image in the object area."
msgstr "<emph>ຕຳແໜ່ງ/ຂະໜາດກຳນົດເອງ</emph>: ຕັ້ງຄ່າຂະໜາດ ແລະ ຕຳແໜ່ງຂອງຮູບພາບໃນພື້ນທີ່ວັດຖຸແບບກຳນົດເອງ."

#. sAiUV
