#: 05220000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05220000.xhp\n"
"par_id3157808\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/textattrtabpage/MTR_FLD_TOP\">Enter the amount of space to leave between the top edge of the drawing or text object and the upper border of the text.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/textattrtabpage/MTR_FLD_TOP\">ປ້ອນປະລິມານໄລຍະຫ່າງທີ່ຕ້ອງການປະໄວ້ລະຫວ່າງຂອບເທິງຂອງວັດຖຸການແຕ້ມ ຫຼື ວັດຖຸຂໍ້ຄວາມ ແລະ ຂອບເທິງຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ.</ahelp>"

#. CvLyK
#: 05220000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05220000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149237\n"
"help.text"
