#. L9FAk
#: 05230000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05230000.xhp\n"
"par_id3157552\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"groessetext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:TransformDialog\">Resizes, moves, rotates, or slants the selected object.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"groessetext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:TransformDialog\">ປ່ຽນຂະໜາດ, ຍ້າຍ, ໝູນ, ຫຼື ເຮັດໃຫ້ວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກອຽງ.</ahelp></variable>"

