"05250100.xhp\n"
"par_id3149991\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:BringToFront\" visibility=\"visible\">Moves the selected object to the top of the stacking order, so that it is in front of other objects.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:BringToFront\" visibility=\"visible\">ຍ້າຍວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກໄປໄວ້ເທິງສຸດຂອງລຳດັບການຊ້ອນກັນ, ເພື່ອໃຫ້ມັນຢູ່ທາງໜ້າວັດຖຸອື່ນໆ.</ahelp>"

