#. 4FEeX
#: 05260100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05260100.xhp\n"
"par_id3150756\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:SetAnchorToPage\">Anchors the selected object so that it always remains on the current page.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:SetAnchorToPage\">ຢຶດວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກເພື່ອໃຫ້ມັນຄົງຢູ່ໃນໜ້າປັດຈຸບັນສະເໝີ.</ahelp>"

#. EN8t8
#: 05260100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05260100.xhp\n"
"par_id781653782304845\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Objects with this anchor can be positioned in relation to the entire page or in relation to the page’s text area."
msgstr "ວັດຖຸທີ່ມີການຢຶດນີ້ສາມາດຈັດຕຳແໜ່ງໄດ້ໂດຍທຽບກັບໜ້າທັງໝົດ ຫຼື ທຽບກັບພື້ນທີ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງໜ້າ."

#. 37QmE
#: 05260100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05260100.xhp\n"
"par_id3149987\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The position of the anchored object on the current page does not change as content and pages are added or removed from the document."
msgstr "ຕຳແໜ່ງຂອງວັດຖຸທີ່ຢຶດໃນໜ້າປັດຈຸບັນຈະບໍ່ປ່ຽນແປງເມື່ອມີການເພີ່ມ ຫຼື ລຶບເນື້ອໃນ ແລະ ໜ້າອອກຈາກເອກະສານ."

#. Z2EuY
#: 05260100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05260100.xhp\n"
"par_id11653782256765\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The current page remains in the document, with its current position in the sequence of pages, as long as the object is anchored to that page."
msgstr "ໜ້າປັດຈຸບັນຈະຍັງຄົງຢູ່ໃນເອກະສານ, ພ້ອມກັບຕຳແໜ່ງປັດຈຸບັນຂອງມັນໃນລຳດັບໜ້າ, ຕາບໃດທີ່ວັດຖຸຍັງຖືກຢຶດໃສ່ໜ້ານັ້ນ."

#. LJDRP
#: 05260100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05260100.xhp\n"
"par_id3152821\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The anchor icon is displayed at the top left corner of the page."
msgstr "ໄອຄອນການຢຶດຈະສະແດງຢູ່ມຸມຊ້າຍເທິງຂອງໜ້າ."

