msgctxt ""
"05260200.xhp\n"
"par_id3155271\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:SetAnchorToPara\" visibility=\"visible\">Anchors the selected object to the current paragraph.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:SetAnchorToPara\" visibility=\"visible\">ຢຶດວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກໃສ່ກັບຢໍ້ໜ້າປັດຈຸບັນ.</ahelp>"

#. MjKEz
#: 05260200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05260200.xhp\n"
"par_id271653783242132\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Objects with this anchor can be positioned in relation to the page or its text area, as well as the paragraph or its text area."
msgstr "ວັດຖຸທີ່ມີການຢຶດນີ້ສາມາດຈັດຕຳແໜ່ງໄດ້ໂດຍທຽບກັບໜ້າ ຫຼື ພື້ນທີ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງມັນ, ລວມທັງຢໍ້ໜ້າ ຫຼື ພື້ນທີ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງຢໍ້ໜ້າ."

#. RSrcL
#: 05260200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05260200.xhp\n"
"par_id3154926\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The anchor icon is displayed at the left page margin at the beginning of the paragraph."
msgstr "ໄອຄອນການຢຶດຈະສະແດງຢູ່ຂອບຊ້າຍຂອງໜ້າໃນຕອນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງຢໍ້ໜ້າ."

#. isPXG
#: 05260200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05260200.xhp\n"
"par_id751654784158415\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"paraposition\">When a paragraph is used for positioning and the paragraph extends over more than one page or column, then positioning options that refer to a <menuitem>paragraph area</menuitem> or <menuitem>paragraph text area</menuitem> are applied only to the portion of the paragraph in the page or column where the anchor is located</variable>."
msgstr "<variable id=\"paraposition\">ເມື່ອໃຊ້ຢໍ້ໜ້າເພື່ອຈັດຕຳແໜ່ງ ແລະ ຢໍ້ໜ້ານັ້ນຂະຫຍາຍອອກຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງໜ້າ ຫຼື ຄໍລຳ, ຕົວເລືອກການຈັດຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ອ້າງເຖິງ <menuitem>ພື້ນທີ່ຢໍ້ໜ້າ</menuitem> ຫຼື <menuitem>ພື້ນທີ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມຢໍ້ໜ້າ</menuitem> ຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້ສະເພາະກັບສ່ວນຂອງຢໍ້ໜ້າໃນໜ້າ ຫຼື ຄໍລຳບ່ອນທີ່ການຢຶດຕັ້ງຢູ່ເທົ່ານັ້ນ</variable>."

#. dkCHz
