#. GBM4J
#: 05290300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05290300.xhp\n"
"par_id3146856\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"betretentext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:EnterGroup\" visibility=\"visible\">Opens the selected group, so that you can edit the individual objects. If the selected group contains nested group, you can repeat this command on the subgroups.</ahelp></variable> This command does not permanently ungroup the objects."
msgstr "<variable id=\"betretentext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:EnterGroup\" visibility=\"visible\">ເປີດກຸ່ມທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂວັດຖຸແຕ່ລະອັນໄດ້. ຖ້າກຸ່ມທີ່ເລືອກມີກຸ່ມຍ່ອຍຊ້ອນຢູ່, ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ຊ້ຳກັບກຸ່ມຍ່ອຍໄດ້.</ahelp></variable> ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ເປັນການຍົກເລີກການຈັດກຸ່ມແບບຖາວອນ."

#. CgMZF
#: 05290300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05290300.xhp\n"
"par_id3157991\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To select an individual object in a group, hold down <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline>, and then click the object."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເລືອກວັດຖຸອັນໃດອັນໜຶ່ງໃນກຸ່ມ, ໃຫ້ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້ ແລ້ວຄລິກໃສ່ວັດຖຸນັ້ນ."

