"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"zeilenhoehetext\"><ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/rowheightdialog/RowHeightDialog\">Changes the height of the current row, or the selected rows.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"zeilenhoehetext\"><ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/rowheightdialog/RowHeightDialog\">ປ່ຽນຄວາມສູງຂອງແຖວປັດຈຸບັນ ຫຼື ແຖວທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້.</ahelp></variable>"

#. ECX9t
#: 05340100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05340100.xhp\n"
"par_id3150756\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"CALC\">You can also change the height of a row by dragging the divider below the row header. To fit the row height to the cell contents, double-click the divider.</caseinline></switchinline>"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"CALC\">ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດປ່ຽນຄວາມສູງຂອງແຖວໄດ້ໂດຍການລາກເສັ້ນແບ່ງທີ່ຢູ່ລຸ່ມຫົວແຖວ. ເພື່ອປັບຄວາມສູງແຖວໃຫ້ພໍດີກັບເນື້ອໃນໃນເຊລ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກສອງບາດໃສ່ເສັ້ນແບ່ງນັ້ນ.</caseinline></switchinline>"

#. zayHR
