#: 05340100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05340100.xhp\n"
"par_id961723888998469\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Automatically adjusts the row height based on the current font."
msgstr "ປັບຄວາມສູງແຖວໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດໂດຍອີງຕາມຟອນປັດຈຸບັນ."

