msgctxt ""
"05340400.xhp\n"
"par_id7812433001\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">Select database records. Drag-and-drop rows or cells to the document to insert contents. Drag-and-drop column headers to insert fields.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"hidden\">ເລືອກຂໍ້ມູນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ. ລາກ ແລະ ວາງແຖວ ຫຼື ເຊລ ລົງໃນເອກະສານເພື່ອແຊກເນື້ອໃນ. ລາກ ແລະ ວາງຫົວຖັນເພື່ອແຊກຟິລ (Fields).</ahelp>"

