"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"svx/ui/docking3deffects/geometry\">Adjusts the shape of the selected 3D object. You can only modify the shape of a 3D object that was created by converting a 2D object. To convert a 2D object to 3D, select the object, right-click, and then choose <emph>Convert - To 3D</emph>, or <emph>Convert - To 3D Rotation Object</emph>.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"svx/ui/docking3deffects/geometry\">ປັບຮູບຮ່າງຂອງວັດຖຸ 3 ມິຕິ ທີ່ເລືອກ. ທ່ານສາມາດປັບຮູບຮ່າງໄດ້ສະເພາະວັດຖຸ 3 ມິຕິ ທີ່ຖືກປ່ຽນມາຈາກ 2 ມິຕິ ເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ເພື່ອປ່ຽນວັດຖຸ 2 ມິຕິ ໃຫ້ເປັນ 3 ມິຕິ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກວັດຖຸ, ຄລິກຂວາ ແລ້ວເລືອກ <emph>ປ່ຽນ - ເປັນ 3 ມິຕິ</emph> ຫຼື <emph>ປ່ຽນ - ເປັນວັດຖຸໝູນ 3 ມິຕິ</emph>.</ahelp>"

