"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"svx/ui/docking3deffects/mode\">Select the shading method that you want to use. Flat shading assigns a single color to a single polygon on the surface of the object. Gouraud shading blends colors across the polygons. Phong shading averages the color of each pixel based on the pixels that surround it, and requires the most processing power.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"svx/ui/docking3deffects/mode\">ເລືອກວິທີການໃຫ້ເງົາທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຊ້. Flat shading ຈະກຳນົດສີດຽວໃຫ້ກັບແຕ່ລະຮູບຫຼາຍແຈເທິງພື້ນຜິວວັດຖຸ. Gouraud shading ຈະປະສົມສີລະຫວ່າງຮູບຫຼາຍແຈ. Phong shading ຈະສະເລ່ຍສີຂອງແຕ່ລະພິກເຊວຕາມພິກເຊວທີ່ຢູ່ອ້ອມຮອບ ເຊິ່ງຕ້ອງໃຊ້ກຳລັງການປະມວນຜົນສູງສຸດ.</ahelp>"

