msgctxt ""
"06130000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153577\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/BasicIDE/ui/basicmacrodialog/assign\">Opens the <link href=\"text/shared/01/06140000.xhp\">Customize</link> dialog, where you can assign the selected macro to a menu command, a toolbar, or an event.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/BasicIDE/ui/basicmacrodialog/assign\">ເປີດໄດອາລັອກ <link href=\"text/shared/01/06140000.xhp\">ປັບແຕ່ງ</link>, ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດມາກໂຄຣທີ່ເລືອກໃຫ້ກັບຄຳສັ່ງເມນູ, ແຖບເຄື່ອງມື, ຫຼື ເຫດການໃດໜຶ່ງ.</ahelp>"

