msgctxt ""
"06130000.xhp\n"
"par_id3154514\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To create a new macro in your document, select the \"Standard\" module in the <emph>Macro from</emph> list, and then click <widget>New</widget>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອສ້າງມາກໂຄຣໃໝ່ໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກໂມດູນ \"Standard\" ໃນລາຍຊື່ <emph>ມາກໂຄຣຈາກ</emph>, ແລ້ວກົດ <widget>ໃໝ່</widget>."

