msgctxt ""
"06130000.xhp\n"
"par_id51571312108555\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To create a new module in a library of the <emph>My Macros</emph> container, select the proper library and press <widget>New</widget>. The $[officename] Basic editor opens."
msgstr "ເພື່ອສ້າງໂມດູນໃໝ່ໃນຫ້ອງສະໝຸດຂອງ <emph>ມາກໂຄຣຂອງຂ້ອຍ</emph>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຫ້ອງສະໝຸດທີ່ເໝາະສົມແລ້ວກົດ <widget>ໃໝ່</widget>. ຕົວແກ້ໄຂ Basic ຂອງ $[officename] ຈະເປີດຂຶ້ນ."

#. dDQiT
