"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/hyphenate/worded\">Displays the hyphenation suggestion(s) for the selected word.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"cui/ui/hyphenate/worded\">ສະແດງຄຳແນະນຳການແຍກພະຍາງສຳລັບຄຳສັບທີ່ເລືອກ.</ahelp>"

#. EBzQg
