#. TNNPb
#: ref_pdf_export.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ref_pdf_export.xhp\n"
"par_id3154044\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"export\"><ahelp hid=\".\">Saves the current file to Portable Document Format (PDF) version 1.4.</ahelp> A PDF file can be viewed and printed on any platform with the original formatting intact, provided that supporting software is installed.</variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"export\"><ahelp hid=\".\">ບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ປັດຈຸບັນເປັນຮູບແບບເອກະສານທີ່ເຄື່ອນຍ້າຍໄດ້ (PDF) ເວີຊັນ 1.4.</ahelp> ໄຟລ໌ PDF ສາມາດເບິ່ງ ແລະ ພິມໄດ້ໃນທຸກລະບົບ ໂດຍທີ່ຮູບແບບຕົ້ນສະບັບຍັງຄົບຖ້ວນ, ພຽງແຕ່ຕ້ອງມີຊອບແວທີ່ຮອງຮັບຕິດຕັ້ງໄວ້.</variable>"

#. NHTF4
#: ref_pdf_export.xhp
