"xformsdatatab.xhp\n"
"par_id636921\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Enter the DOM node to bind the control model to. Click the <emph>...</emph> button for a dialog to enter the XPath expression.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ປ້ອນ DOM node ເພື່ອເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບແມ່ແບບການຄວບຄຸມ. ຄລິກທີ່ປຸ່ມ <emph>...</emph> ເພື່ອເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບເພື່ອປ້ອນນິພົດ XPath.</ahelp>"

